@Node Main "File Management"
@ToC "Ww3.guide/Main"
 @{B}CONTENTS@{UB}

 This section provides help about storing and
 opening your documents, creating new documents
 and how to finish your session with Wordworth.

   @{" Creating A New Document " Link "Files.guide/NewDoc"}
   @{" Creating A Separate Document Disk " Link "Files.guide/NewDocDisk"}

   @{" Opening A Previously Saved Document " Link "Files.guide/OpenDoc"}
   @{" Opening A Document From A Separate Floppy Disk " Link "Files.guide/OpenDocDisk"}

   @{" Deleting A Document " Link "Files.guide/DeleteDoc"}
   @{" Closing Your Document " Link "Files.guide/CloseDoc"}

   @{" Saving Your Document " Link "Files.guide/SaveDoc"}
